 24 May 2015 Minister in the Presidency for Planning Monitoring and Evaluation, Mr Jeff Radebe, will address media on the outcomes of the Cabinet meeting held today (24 June 2015) in Cape Town. Minister Radebe will be joined by Minister of Trade and Industry Rob Davis. The media briefing will take place as follows: Date: Thursday, 25 June 2015 Time: 10h00 Venue: Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Parliament, Cape Town NB: There will be a video link to GCIS Head Office, Tshedimosetso House, 1035 Francis Baard, Hatfield, Pretoria RSVP: Pheliswa Sebati (Pretoria) Cell: 082 413 4609 E-mail: pheliswa@gcis.gov.za Andile Duka (Cape Town) Cell: 071 154 5619 E-mail: andile@gcis.gov.za Enquiries: Phumla Williams, Acting Cabinet Spokesperson Cell: 083 501 0139